Nafesha Veronica Richardson (amụrụ n'afọ 1996) onye guzobere Spark SVG bụ onye na-agbachitere ikike ndị ntorobịa si St Vincent na Grenadines
Nafesha bụ onye otu Ndị ntorobịa Gender na nha nhata netwọkụ nke Commonwealth (CYGEN), onye mmeri ndị ntorobịa nke nkwekọrịta Escazú, ma bụrụkwa onye ọrụ afọ ofufo na St
Vincent na Grenadines Girl Guides Association.
A mụrụ Nafesha Richarson n'afọ 1996 na St Vincent na Grenadines
A zụlitere Nafesha na St Vincent na Grenadines, obodo dị na mpaghara Latin America na Caribbean (LAC)
Ọ gụsịrị akwụkwọ na Bachelors nke Iwu na Mahadum nke West Indies n'afọ 2020. Ugbu a, ọ na-agbaso Usoro mmụta Liberal Education na Hugh Wooding Law School.
Mgbe ọ dị afọ asaa, Nafesha Richardson banyere St

Vincent na Grenadines Òtù Ndị Nduzi Nwanyị nke Geraldines dị ka onye ọrụ afọ ofufo iji mụta ma lụso nsogbu mmekọrịta mmadụ na ibe ya na nsogbu ime ụlọ ọgụ nke na-emetụta ndị St Vincent na Grenadines ndị a na-abụkarị ime ihe ike n'ụlọ na mmekọahụ. N'ọnwa Mee afọ 2019 mgbe ọ dị afọ iri abụọ na abụọ, Nafesha hiwere Spark St Vincent na Grenadines (Spark SVG) na ebumnuche nke ịkpali, inye ike na ịkpali ndị na-eto eto na Saint Vincent na Grenadines iji mee mgbanwe dị mma na obodo ha. Ọ gara Commonwealth Banquet n'afọ 2020 ya na Julius Karl D

N'ọnwa Machị, afọ 2020, a nabatara Nafesha n'etiti ndị mmeri ise nke nkwekọrịta Escazú. N'afọ 2020, o so na ndị isi ndị ntorobịa bụ ndị otu Ndị ntorobịa Gender na nha nhata netwokụ nke Commonwealth (CYGEN) iji malite mkpọsa "#Reform53 - Ọnụ maka nha nha nke iwu". Na Septemba 2020, e nyere ya Commonwealth Point Of Light Award maka ọrụ ya na Sparks SVG. N'otu afọ ahụ, ọ na-aghọ otu n'ime Women Deliver Young Leader
